	(text "This goes to the front right side PCB, which has the system \npower button and a power LED. The PCB also has a USB 2.0\nsplitter, but that is not dealt with on this backplane;\nit will plug straight into the motherboard. 3 pins are for 5V\nto support higher current draw."
